name: Pastel+lines mix
description:
1.0

令人兴奋的画面质感,经过了无数次的重复尝试我确定了这款模型的合成公式，

配方 (0.675pastelMix + 0.325chikmix)

Exciting picture, after countless repeated attempts, I determined the composite formula of this model.

Formula (0.675pastelMix + 0.325chikmix)

VAE：pastel-waifu-diffusion.vae

_________________________________________________________________________

我想要鲜艳的颜色但也需要勾勒出清晰的衣服质感，于是在数十种合成配方中删选出了这一款，

配方(0.8pastelMix + (0.5perfectWorld + 0.5chikmix))+0.02chikmix

图片中使用lora为

Chinese fashion girl

使用参数为0.7

ps:pastelMix真的是一款伟大的模型

I wanted bright colors, but I also needed to outline the texture of the clothes, so I chose this one from dozens of synthetic recipes.

Formula (0.8pastelMix + (0.5perfectWorld + 0.5chikmix))+0.02chikmix.

Lora is used in the picture as.

Chinese fashion girl.

The usage parameter is 0.7.

Ps:pastelMix is really a great model.
